# Web3Forms access key — get yours at https://web3forms.com
# 1. Sign up and verify your email inbox
# 2. Copy your Access Key into a local .env file (not this example file)
# 3. Restart dev server: npm run dev
# 4. In Web3Forms dashboard, allow localhost for testing if domain restriction is enabled
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your_access_key_here
